  "3211850": {
    "name": "星萼",
    "steam_appid": 3211850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/47c239093eb737739d83580138ecc82a.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/9bbf218359d1b33d9ba5bc7559b9a3a1.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/9bbf218359d1b33d9ba5bc7559b9a3a1.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/9bbf218359d1b33d9ba5bc7559b9a3a1.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款结合了即时战略和基地建设元素的游戏，其中加入了一种全新的敌人——星萼。星萼是一群强大的植物外星人，如果不加以控制，它们会迅速蔓延并控制地图上的大片区域。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/60f9c1ecd994f881f91e8e7f3cab67e7.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/2586718864db28b84fa4d8bda2c5a497.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/2586718864db28b84fa4d8bda2c5a497.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/2586718864db28b84fa4d8bda2c5a497.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您是阿瓦里斯公司深空采矿船上的最后一名幸存者，被送到了一颗贫瘠星球的轨道上。您挣扎着想从长达一个世纪的冷冻中苏醒，可还未恢复元气就被发射到了星球地表，收到舰船AI下达的开采矿石的指令。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您需要建设能源网络，部署采集车，提炼矿石并将其送往轨道换取信用币。同时还要筑起围墙和炮塔保卫基地，部署坦克和火炮将星萼击退，遏止它们的长势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请合理分配基地的能源需求，确保关键防御设施不断电。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取稀有矿藏以提升采矿和军事能力。连接增益建筑可获得额外的电力、采矿和治疗加成。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/5fe8795ea5f8c3d32a763a9f769e3f05.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f19957e7d8e610c389b23fb294686a49.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f19957e7d8e610c389b23fb294686a49.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f19957e7d8e610c389b23fb294686a49.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您会选择打造铜墙铁壁的防御工事，还是在星萼扩散到家门口前先发制人？是固守阵地并构建强大的兵力，还是采用灵活机动的战术打法？有很多方法击败不同的星萼变种。您可以自由选择基地的初始位置，尝试不同战术策略，不断摸索并应对各种情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/dcf116c3e509f231728aac47ce8b8ad3.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/a03e53b81c948a7934d00f0b0f87ef95.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/a03e53b81c948a7934d00f0b0f87ef95.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/a03e53b81c948a7934d00f0b0f87ef95.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护数据档案库以获取研究点数，并利用科技树解锁和升级更高级的单位和建筑。解锁炼狱火焰喷射器，将星萼燃烧殆尽！建造单位工坊，制造配备了多门炮塔的巨型坦克，并利用悬浮技术提升其速度。解锁轨道技术，从轨道发射毁灭性的激光束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/386e84f2a03b8f2ba04036a6d9d0ff3b.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/bc07b25088b9569d0716584523298dd3.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/bc07b25088b9569d0716584523298dd3.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/bc07b25088b9569d0716584523298dd3.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护并启动通讯阵列，接入集团的深空网络。扫描星萼的根瘤，了解这些敌对生命体的运作方式。在争夺星球控制权并寻找回家之路的过程中，发现全新且危险的星萼变种！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/cf55aff035fe8578f5f457ec65015ddc.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/1f98e62e3a738daa96ea352a309429df.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/1f98e62e3a738daa96ea352a309429df.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/1f98e62e3a738daa96ea352a309429df.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抢先体验战役：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教程及 16 张地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 个难度级别</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科技树</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚取研究点数并解锁新科技</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级单位和建筑物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎战 5 种星萼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心邪恶的清算者 AI！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重复游玩遭遇战模式：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 张地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 个难度级别</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置星萼根瘤的数量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择初始资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配置可用矿场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择您的科技水平并生成布局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友分享种子即可挑战同样的关卡</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f656c6175623d4698372012b00189e4e.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/24e342a8eac0d25845fc1826d7ef7016.avif?t=1771356239\" width=780 height=1224 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/d2fcd2d00a824fb635b7c4295b814c31.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星萼》目前处于抢先体验阶段，我们非常希望能听到您的想法，帮助我们确定未来的开发方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎访问玩家论坛或加入我们的Discord频道，说出您的想法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f1d8b12d8ab3773cc843d5e0635dfc0d.poster.avif?t=1771356239\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f1d8b12d8ab3773cc843d5e0635dfc0d.webm?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211850/extras/f1d8b12d8ab3773cc843d5e0635dfc0d.mp4?t=1771356239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
